      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, representing a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-compression valvetrain. The double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled with upgraded seals and cryo-treated hub bolts to ensure precise cam timing. Structural integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the factory-spec bushings maintain original torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with a short-throw shifter, feeding a GKN variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for optimal contact patches under lateral load. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including recent rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive fluid flush using high-viscosity synthetics. It is a mechanically flawless, turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
